Common.Highlight.Common.Text: State of the art, near new building
Great access to Monash Fwy & Eastlink

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located in The Pellicano Group’s prestigious Innovation Park, this recently built 3,432sqm* office/warehouse will be highly sought after for its location, quality design, staff amenity and huge hardstand area.

Innovation Park is home to globally recognised brands including; Aldi, Cyclone & Dexion, who have all selected Innovation Park for its connectivity to wider Melbourne via Eastlink (M3) and the Monash Freeway (M1).

The business park also benefits from first class amenities with several cafés and restaurants in the immediate vicinity including the Bricklane Micro Brewery off Jayco Drive. 

Property features:
+ 372sqm* dual level corporate office
+ 3,060sqm* of high clearance, clear span warehouse
+ Huge hardstand area 
+ 3 container height roller doors 
+ 32m full length side drive (15m-20m is industry standard)
+ Full length 8m canopy cover
+ B Double compliant access
+ 46 on-site car spaces  

*approx.
